Title: Fix sorting by folder on ruleset pages
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1661440677
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0b1

The rules on ruleset pages were always sorted by folder ID.
If the folder was renamed this could lead to a wrong sorting order.

Now the title path is used.

